  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improve the education of 2,000 students in Kenya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kenyan schools are buckling under the weight of growing student bodies and stagnating government funding. Hopeful Africa endeavors to partner with schools in Kenya, listen to their needs, and do its best to provide the financial support necessary to increase the quality of education given to Kenya&apos;s children. By providing teacher support and funding, student sponsorships, and materials such as books, computers, or electricity, Hopeful Africa is helping 2,000 students reach better education.</narrative>
  </description>
